reviewText: I was hoping this was the PBS series on the Italian Ameticans-a historic  series. It is not that at all and I am very disappointed. I am thinking of returning it- something I have never done with an Amazon purchase.
The only problem is that both films use a lot of the same interviews and film clips, so they are very similar! they are still very interesting!
A gift for my father. He came to the States when he was 14. He loved it!
